三月 25, 2018 11:56:57 下午 no.dict.data.Dictionary putIntoError
警告: word: 
syllabel: 
sound: 
clazz: 
examples: oppslagsord at
/at /
underordningsord (subjunksjon)
Engelsk that
subordinating conj
 introduces nominal clauses
Engelsk I saw him arriving
 are you sure he will be coming
Engelsk I can understand that you're tired
